comments: Towns (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in Hill's (MIL) path and gives Hill a step of distance to avoid the contact.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Russell (MIN) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Allen (MIL) and Vanderbilt (MIN) make incidental arm contact with one another during rebounding.
Beverley (MIN) and Middleton (MIL) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Vanderbilt (MIN) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Beverley (MIN) extends his right arm forward and makes clean contact with the ball during Middleton's (MIL) driving shot attempt.
Edwards (MIN) contests the put-back attempt and incidental "high-five" contact occurs with Middleton (MIL) after he tips the ball up.
Towns (MIN) and Connaughton (MIL) engage and disengage with one another as they move around the screen.
Hill (MIL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Hill (MIL) is bringing his arm into a vertical position and absorbs the contact made with Edwards (MIN) as Edwards jumps away from the basket during the driving shot attempt.
Vanderbilt (MIN) and Connaughton (MIL) make incidental body contact with one another during rebounding.

Russell (MIN) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the contact made with Middleton (MIL) during the drive. As Russell absorbs the contact, his left hand brushes Middleton's arm and marginal contact occurs.
Vanderbilt (MIN) moves forward toward Middleton (MIL) and marginal arm contact occurs after Middleton picks up his dribble.
Middleton (MIL) takes another dribble after gathering the ball, which was dislodged by Vanderbilt.
Vanderbilt (MIN) legally contests Connaughton's (MIL) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Russell (MIN) swipes forward and cleanly dislodges the ball away from Nwora (MIL).
Russell (MIN) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Beverley (MIN) and Middleton (MIL) come together at the same spot as they move over the screen and marginal body contact occurs.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) firms up in his screening position in Beverley's (MIN) path and absorbs the side-to-side contact.
Beverley (MIN) legally contests Middleton's (MIL) jump shot attempt.
Middleton (MIL) maintains a legal guarding position as he moves in a direct path toward the basket and absorbs the body contact initiated by Edwards (MIN) on the driving shot attempt.
Connaughton (MIL) and Towns (MIN) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.
Middleton (MIL) initiates contact with Edwards' (MIN) left arm, affecting Edwards' SQBR after he receives the inbound.
Edwards (MIN) turns alongside Hill's (MIL) path and marginal body contact occurs as Hill dribbles up the floor.
Towns (MIN) retreats away from Hill (MIL) and legally contests his driving shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes incidental body contact with Beverley (MIN) as they each attempt to retrieve the rebound.
Beverley (MIN) saves the ball back into play before landing out of bounds.
Allen (MIL) commits a take foul on Russell (MIN).
Vanderbilt (MIN) and Towns (MIN) legally contest Middleton's (MIL) jump shot attempt.
